<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.sterll.claude_terminal</id>

  <name>Claude Terminal</name>
  <summary>Manage Claude Code projects with an integrated terminal and AI chat</summary>

  <metadata_license>MIT</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-3.0-only</project_license>

  <description>
    <p>
      Claude Terminal is a desktop application for developers who use Claude Code.
      It provides a unified workspace to manage multiple projects, run terminals,
      chat with Claude via the Agent SDK, and handle git operations â€” all in one place.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Multi-project management with folder hierarchy and quick actions</li>
      <li>Integrated terminal (xterm.js with WebGL rendering)</li>
      <li>Claude AI chat with Agent SDK streaming support</li>
      <li>Git panel with staging, commits, inline diff, stash and worktrees</li>
      <li>Time tracking with per-project statistics and charts</li>
      <li>Skills and agents marketplace</li>
      <li>MCP server management</li>
      <li>Remote control via WebSocket with QR code authentication</li>
      <li>French and English interface</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.sterll.claude_terminal.desktop</launchable>

